Name: Golden Dungeons
About the game: Golden Dungeons - is a simple hardcore platformer game, the goal to get out of the cave. The game may seem simple, but some levels so hard, and you need a lot of free time to pass it's. It will bring a challenge to your skill, reaction, and adaptability. Sometimes the levels will not seem to be passable, but we have always way out ... Features: Simple controls Pleasant music. Over 25+ levels. Secrets and bonus levels. Hardcore gameplay. More than 3 hours of gameplay Nothing superfluous, enjoy the game!
